  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To Assess the impact of therapeutic education on:

        -  the occurrence of long term diabetes complications .

        -  balance of his diabetes
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      evaluation of the benefits of therapeutic education by:

        -  glycated hemoglobin assay

        -  telephone monitoring

        -  quiz

        -  monitoring of adverse event related to diabete
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
