    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria: Patients

          -  diabetic

          -  hospitalized in Léon Berard

          -  with telephone line

          -  written consent given

          -  belong to a social security system

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  no diabetics

          -  patient having alredy completing a therapeutic education program

          -  minor patient (&lt;18 years)

          -  pregnant woman

          -  without telephone line

          -  no belong to a social security system

          -  patient alredy inclued on clinical study.

          -  patient tutelage or under curatorship
      </textblock>
